Linter
Static analysis consists of using tools that analyze your source code looking for errors, lack of adherence to rules or conventions, or other potential problems.
Different linter tools for different languages
our project has javascript and Node so
we choose ESLint + Prettier for JS

1)ESLint Install
npm install eslint --save-dev
2)Initializing

npx eslint --init
check syntax, find problems and enforce code style.
JavaScript modules 


3)Using ESLint to Check a File
npx eslint path-to-your-file.js


